summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 77646, appropriating money from the Seattle Sewer Bonds 1946 Fund in aid of the improvement of 40th Avenue West from Hooker Street to a point approximately 320 feet south of Sheridan Street, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by constructing sewers and otherwise improving the same, as authorized by Ordinance No. 77645, creating Local Improvement District No. 5893.
